So delighted that you chose to make Birmingham, Al your new headquarters. You come at a magnificent time, as Birmingham is growing and redeveloping beyond all expectations. Now Joonko will be joining in with all of the growth and excitement. Again, welcome.....home.

Haters can hate and try all they can to decry Birmingham, Al. But, this city that is known for its place in Civil Rights is no longer a secret. Now San Francisco based Joonko is relocating its headquarters to Birmingham, Al...to the disappointment and to the dismay of the haters.

Birmingham lead the US during the civil rights era on fighting for D&I. It's a point of pride. We lead w/it. It resonates.
